rows.label: tlk45450111_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Chairman Bahn told you where to go,
didn't he? Down to the Exit Dock, on
the starboard side of Goldmund.

rows.label: tlk45450111_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Once you've sorted out what you're
doing with your advance payment, you
should head down there sharpish.
